External Knowledge: 
- The average rating is used as a measure of a movie's quality or popularity; 
- The rating rank is a way to compare the relative quality or popularity of movies; 
- The campaign information provides insight into the marketing efforts for each movie.

sql:
SELECT movie_id, SUM(total_gross) AS total_gross, SUM(opening_weekend_theaters) AS total_theaters
FROM box_office
GROUP BY movie_id;

SELECT m.movie_title
FROM movies m
JOIN box_office bo ON m.movie_id = bo.movie_id
WHERE bo.total_gross > (
    SELECT AVG(total_gross) FROM box_office
);
